      "message": "Since it’s possible to call Open() on an already-opened DirectoryReader, either:\n\n - Make it be not possible (DCHECK(!dir_.is_valid())?), or\n - Set no_more_files_ \u003d false on any entry to Open()\n\nWindows too. (Another field to worry about there, too, if you choose the second option.)",
